mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92c6cdead095a1c5be0e553fd3f73ed46cfd612","tid":495844,"uid":1009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上年做六弟, 就話排名唔撚重要, 有三冠勁過晒第2,3,4,5<br />\n今年就調返轉頭, 好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nJ撚左成年摩二季，結果仆哂街淨係識拉車利落水，對住曼城就粒聲唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2252672c844a2416d7895ab0b308fb243716e01","tid":495844,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上年做六弟, 就話排名唔撚重要, 有三冠勁過晒第2,3,4,5<br />\n今年就調返轉頭, 好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nJ撚左成年摩二季，結果仆哂街淨係識拉車利落水，對住曼城就粒聲唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班撚樣日日喺狗竇叫人黑鏝<br />\n但又唔敢開拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f3eeffb0e9c3cc0eb7c794cb7e0cf3eef4477f","tid":495844,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上年做六弟, 就話排名唔撚重要, 有三冠勁過晒第2,3,4,5<br />\n今年就調返轉頭, 好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nJ撚左成年摩二季，結果仆哂街淨係識拉車利落水，對住曼城就粒聲唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地咁撚勁點出到聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一陣比人撚返轉頭就搞到要搵媽咪幫手就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <blockquote>引用</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5d9b0f3163c2e075b04874a05f77be820a19b0